Images: ["[630_360_16843...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1684329795-206.jpeg)", "[1684329795-18...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1684329795-182.jpeg)", "[1684329796-96...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1684329796-965.jpeg)", "[1684329795-25...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1684329795-253.jpeg)"]

Tags: ['Ліс', 'Відпочинок', 'Юрій Болоховець']

Type: Article

